data.description: Look no further! This amazing home offers everything! With 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a cozy fireplace, granite countertops, an eat-in kitchen, a spacious great room, a secure gated courtyard, abundant closet space and storage options, it's a true gem. The home also features a tile roof, brand-new energy-efficient dual-pane windows, a luxurious jet tub and a walk-in shower in the master suite, and a generous walk-in master closet. To top it all off, this home has a RV gate with an extended wide driveway for extra parking.  And int he backyard, hidden beneath the deck is a pool that, while currently drained, adds so much possibilities to the outdoor space. . Don't wait; this exceptional property will not stay on the market for long!
